<p><strong>哈弗大狗</strong></p>
<p><strong>潮玩上市，闪耀来袭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201016/112f7f67e8e5447980fbbc789d307ddb.png" max-width="600" /></p>
